overview: One of the best flicks to come out of Jet Set Team Productions, College Jocks 3: The Competition will satisfy fans of both the studio as well as other porn lovers. Set in a gym the story revolves around a group of very tightly knit body builders who meet every Saturday to spot one another at the Hollywood Gym. Stuart is the new guy, the one who hasn't yet been inducted into the group's workout rituals. Pornstars: Nino Bacci, Justin Mycles, Cody Prescott, Niko Reeves, Jeb Stuart
title: College Jocks 3: The Competition
